{"tid":454501,"cid":27,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇一班廢青想一齊做運動減肥？","createTime":"2017-11-01T07:30:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-01T16:57:45.000Z","uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d12b354d002b371b9449a7e3cfa36d9637437dad","tid":454501,"uid":92200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T07:30:26.000Z","msg":"我相信好多人都知道做運動嘅好處，特別係跑步<br />\n跑步係帶氧運動，對你身體各種功能都帶來好處，亦都可以燃燒脂肪<br />\n最重要個人跑完步，長期落去個人諗野都正面啲，專注力堅持力都加強<br />\n<br />\n不過咁多好處但就無咩人堅持做到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因為大多藉口比自己去拒絕 &quot; 聽日先跑 &quot; / &quot; 唔得閒 / 落雨 &quot;<br />\n所以我想整個活動，自問廢青嘅你地，交出一個心愛重要嘅物品比我作為參加條件<br />\n我就會幫你保管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n咁你就要定期Report運動量 (一星期至少跑2-3次跑) (用Apps顯示)<br />\n如果做唔到，就要扣分！<br />\n（當然可以同我傾下點解做唔到～係咪有困難心事）<br />\n當扣到咁上下，你嘅物品就會捐出去有需要嘅人～<br />\n為期兩個月，最好定一定個目標比自己<br />\n有冇人想Ｊｏｉｎ<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果自己一個跑好悶，時間許可又夾到，可以約我或其他參加者一齊跑步<br />\n我諗到個活動名就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 《心愛物品要靠運動來還》<br />\n<br />\nPS 比個物品真係相對重要D，唔好比D 唔知咩野出來 博捐出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://goo.gl/forms/yjzQ4cl9SaFtQ75A2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2Fforms%2FyjzQ4cl9SaFtQ75A2&d=iDWYYGGuCy9Wb6HPCWE4tARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=60fe0da3\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/forms/yjzQ4cl9SaFtQ75A2</a><br />\nGoogle form報名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/sw369\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsw369&d=iDWYYGGuCy9Wb6HPCWE4tARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=fb147402\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sw369</a><br />\n有咩問都可以搵我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"705d900b59d5de06d653f844963204bf948f7e29","tid":454501,"uid":127033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:14:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a0ffcc205ef063a5cd2b61fae1b8f26fb56b0bb","tid":454501,"uid":19657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T08:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4008433002c9d5d0d1be005e9bc524d7b366bbfe","tid":454501,"uid":20057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:54:31.000Z","msg":"約出黎做運動無問題 <br />\n但如果要人逼先去做 呢個無自律<br />\n我唔認同樓主幫人keep野呢個做法"},{"pid":"d2d21ebded69f4b98b7295794cf118e0b56a20f4","tid":454501,"uid":15471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:56:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89ebee7a3a36019f3b5039838cfee9b821466b18","tid":454501,"uid":144,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-01T16:57:45.000Z","msg":"招fd子?🚬"}]}